imdb.plot outline: Each week on MYX TV's Top 10 music video countdown show viewers can watch their favorite YouTube celebrities talk about the most popular music videos for that week. Celebrities like AJ Raphael, Erika David, Just Kidding Films, Michelle Martinez, and Joey Diamond can be seen guest hosting the show.
